Additional Use Grant

FREE USE (no license required):

You MAY use the Licensed Work without a commercial license for:
- Internal business operations (your own company's use)
- Development, testing, evaluation
- Self-hosted deployment for your organization
- Up to ONE (1) SAP system landscape with up to FIVE (5) environments
  (e.g., sandbox, development, quality, production, training)

This applies regardless of whether your organization is commercial or non-profit.

COMMERCIAL LICENSE REQUIRED:

You MUST obtain a commercial license to:
- Connect more than one SAP system landscape
- Offer as hosted/managed service to third parties
- Build competing products or platforms
- Resell, sublicense, or white-label
- Deploy for multiple legal entities (clients, customers)

---

Multi-Client Licensing

Each end-client (legal entity) requires a separate license when YOU deploy
or manage S4Kit on their behalf.

Examples:
- Your company, 1 SAP system (5 environments) → FREE (no license)
- Your company, 3 SAP systems → Commercial license required
- Consultant deploys for 5 clients → 5 commercial licenses (one per client)
- MSP/Agency hosts for customers → Commercial license per customer

Sharing a single license across multiple legal entities is prohibited.

